body.p: This page is derived from the pcsl sign list's coverage of:

dl.dd: CP 12550-12686 are Archaic Cuneiform Numerals; 12690-12E10 are AP24; For AP23 characters which were dropped in AP24 and not picked up in ACN, the codepoints F2580-F2EC6 are used, i.e., AP23 CP + 0xE0000. F005F-F012D are Oracc PUA entries for PCSL. 0xF3000+ are candidate additions to PC25.
